item.title: about
item.description: Eternity is a minimalist Hugo theme designed for portfolio sites with a fresh feel. This is demo site for Eternity theme. All images are taken from Unsplash. Features Configurable features. Multiple images support. Clean, fresh, minimalist. Integrated lazy load. Automatically creates resized thumbnails.
